rating_comment:
The house we were given was in Shekhertek, Mohammadpur, Dhaka. It is a three bedroom house with three double beds, lounge and kitchen. Bedrooms have un-suit bathroom.
We booked the house for three nights and we are happy to give 3.75 out of 5 stars.

rating_comment: The behavior of the house keeper was outstanding. Overall everything was pretty much good. I personally recommend that anyone can use this apartment as their own.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · December 2023,  · Stayed one night

rating_comment: We had a wonderful stay at this cozy and charming airbnb in Mohammadpur. The host was very friendly and helpful, and the place was clean, comfortable, and secured. The location was perfect for exploring the city, with easy access to public transportation and many attractions. I would highly recommend this airbnb to anyone looking for a relaxing and convenient place to stay in this area. Thanks for everything, KH! You were amazing.
